* applying filters
* resolving selectedIds
* preparing export datasets
* preparing export payloads

====================================================================
PUB/SUB PAYLOAD MODEL
=====================

Google Pub/Sub is the transport mechanism.

Producer services will publish:

* export metadata
* column headers
* export data

Payload may contain:

{
"jobId": "...",
"screenName": "...",
"fileType": "CSV/EXCEL",
"columnHeaders": [...],
"records": [...],
"requestedBy": "...",
"metadata": {...}
}

IMPORTANT:

* column headers are already provided
* records are already prepared
* framework should NOT regenerate business datasets
* framework should NOT modify incoming payload structure

